@startuml SuperAdmin_UC01-40_Configurer_Systeme
title UC-01-40: Configurer Systeme - SuperAdmin (Tous Scenarios)

actor SuperAdmin as SA
participant Dashboard
participant Systeme
participant DB
participant Logs

SA -> Dashboard: 1. Accede a Configuration Systeme
activate Dashboard

Dashboard -> DB: 2. Recupere parametres systeme actuels (securite, tarifs, integrations)
activate DB

alt Erreur BD
  DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Impossible charger config
  deactivate DB
  Dashboard --> SA: ERREUR 500: Config indisponible
  deactivate Dashboard
else BD disponible
  DB --> Dashboard: Retourne parametres
  deactivate DB

  Dashboard --> SA: 3. Affiche menu configuration
  deactivate Dashboard

  SA -> Dashboard: 4. Clique Parametres Tarifs
  activate Dashboard

  Dashboard -> DB: 5. Recupere plans d'abonnement et tarifs (prix TVAC, description, limites)
  activate DB
  DB --> Dashboard: Retourne plans et tarifs
  deactivate DB

  Dashboard --> SA: 6. Affiche formulaire tarifs avec plans (Basic, Pro, Enterprise, etc.)
  deactivate Dashboard

  SA -> Dashboard: 7. Modifie prix Basic plan (€50 TVAC -> €60 TVAC) et clique Verifier
  activate Dashboard

  Dashboard -> Systeme: 8. Valide prix (format decimal, positif, TVA incluse)
  activate Systeme

  alt Prix invalide
    Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Format prix invalide
    deactivate Systeme
    Dashboard --> SA: ERREUR: Prix doit etre positif avec TVA
    deactivate Dashboard
  else Prix valide
    deactivate Systeme

    Dashboard -> Systeme: 9. Verifie impact changement tarif (coherence plans, prix croissants)
    activate Systeme

    Systeme -> Systeme: 10. Valide: Basic < Pro < Enterprise

    Systeme --> Dashboard: Tarifs valides et coherents
    deactivate Systeme

    Dashboard --> SA: 11. Affiche resume changements tarifs
    deactivate Dashboard

    SA -> Dashboard: 12. Clique Appliquer Changements
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> DB: 13. Met a jour tarifs avec transaction atomique
    activate DB

    alt Transaction echouee
      DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Transaction echouee
      deactivate DB
      Dashboard --> SA: ERREUR: Impossible sauvegarder tarifs
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Transaction OK
      DB -> DB: 14. CREATE BACKUP tarifs anciens (pour rollback possible)

      DB -> DB: 15. UPDATE plans tarifs (TVAC, limites secretariats par plan, limites users)

      DB -> DB: 16. INSERT log modification (SuperAdmin, changements, timestamp, version)

      DB --> Dashboard: Tarifs mises a jour
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> DB: 17. Enregistre log audit: Modification tarifs (admin, changements, timestamp)
      activate DB
      DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre en BD
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> Logs: 18. Log event: Tarifs mises a jour
      activate Logs
      Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
      deactivate Logs

      Dashboard --> SA: 19. SUCCES! Tarifs mises a jour\nEffectifs immediatement pour nouveaux abonnements
      deactivate Dashboard

      note over SA, Logs
        **TARIFS MISES A JOUR OK:**
        - Plans modifies (Basic, Pro, Enterprise)
        - Backup ancien tarif cree
        - DB: Audit logs persistes
        - Logs: Events loggues
      end note
    end

    SA -> Dashboard: 20. Clique Parametres Securite
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> DB: 21. Recupere parametres securite (duree session, 2FA, limites login)
    activate DB
    DB --> Dashboard: Retourne parametres securite
    deactivate DB

    Dashboard --> SA: 22. Affiche formulaire securite
    deactivate Dashboard

    SA -> Dashboard: 23. Change duree session 8h -> 4h, clique Appliquer
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> Systeme: 24. Valide parametres securite (duree entre 15min et 24h)
    activate Systeme

    alt Parametres invalides
      Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Duree session invalide
      deactivate Systeme
      Dashboard --> SA: ERREUR: Duree doit etre entre 15min et 24h
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Parametres valides
      deactivate Systeme

      Dashboard -> DB: 25. Met a jour duree session
      activate DB
      DB --> Dashboard: Parametre mis a jour
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> DB: 26. Enregistre log audit: Modification config securite (admin, parametre, ancien, nouveau, timestamp)
      activate DB
      DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> Logs: 27. Log event: Config securite mise a jour
      activate Logs
      Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
      deactivate Logs

      Dashboard --> SA: 28. SUCCES! Securite mise a jour\nNouvelle duree session: 4h
      deactivate Dashboard

      note over SA, Logs
        **SECURITE OK:**
        - Duree session: 4h
        - DB: Audit logs persistes
        - Logs: Events loggues
      end note
    end

    SA -> Dashboard: 29. Clique Parametres Integrations
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> DB: 30. Recupere cles API stockees (Stripe, MinIO, Better Auth) - affiche masquees
    activate DB
    DB --> Dashboard: Retourne cles (affichage securise)
    deactivate DB

    Dashboard --> SA: 31. Affiche formulaire integrations avec cles masquees
    deactivate Dashboard

    SA -> Dashboard: 32. Renouvelle cle API Stripe (rotation securite), clique Appliquer
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> Systeme: 33. Valide nouvelle cle (teste connexion Stripe)
    activate Systeme

    alt Cle Stripe invalide
      Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Cle invalide ou Stripe unreachable
      deactivate Systeme
      Dashboard --> SA: ERREUR: Impossible verifier cle Stripe
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Cle valide
      Systeme -> Systeme: 34. Verifie authentification avec API Stripe

      Systeme --> Dashboard: Cle valide OK
      deactivate Systeme

      Dashboard -> DB: 35. Remplace cle API Stripe en base (chiffree avec encryption)
      activate DB

      DB -> DB: 36. INSERT log rotation cle (admin, service: Stripe, timestamp)

      DB --> Dashboard: Cle mise a jour
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> DB: 37. Enregistre log audit: Rotation cle API (admin, service: Stripe, timestamp)
      activate DB
      DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre en BD
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> Logs: 38. Log event: Rotation cle API OK
      activate Logs
      Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
      deactivate Logs

      Dashboard --> SA: 39. SUCCES! Cle Stripe renouvelée\nAncienne cle: desactivee\nNouvelle cle: active
      deactivate Dashboard

      note over SA, Logs
        **CLE STRIPE OK:**
        - Cle renouvelée OK
        - Ancienne cle revoquee
        - Stripe integration active
        - DB: Audit logs persistes
        - Logs: Events loggues
      end note
    end
  end
end

@enduml
